title: ClosetMaid Bamboo Storage Cabinet, Freestanding Floor Cabinet with Single Door, 3 Shelves, for Bathroom, Living Room, Slide Table, Natural Finish
description: Keep your space organized in a sustainable way with the ClosetMaid Bamboo Storage Cabinet. This cabinet unit offers versatility and function in one convenient organizer. Use in your bathroom to store toiletries, towels, and other supplies. Or place this cabinet next to your couch or sofa as a side table for lamps, books, and décor. The two upper shelves feature ventilated shelves with slats, that both match the cabinet door. Conceal or protect items in the cabinet area with the open storage space. With a bamboo construction, this freestanding cabinet offers strength and durability. It also provides a neutral, natural color to fit right into your home’s décor. Organize your space with ClosetMaid.
